2011-08-25T09:42:32Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/u-k-stocks-decline-vodafone-astrazeneca-fall-as-barclays-shares-climb.html
U.K. stocks fell, reversing a rally
on the benchmark FTSE 100 Index, as Admiral Group Plc and Shire
Plc retreated. The gauge lost 17.23, or 0.3 percent, to 5,188.62
as of 10:41 a.m. in  London , having earlier risen as much as 0.9
percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
